%20It's%20making%20my%20life%20unstable%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20something%20nobody%20wants.%20With%20two%20kids%20to%20raise%2C%20I%20want%20stability%20in%20my%20life%20so%20I%20can%20raise%20them%20in%20a%20proper%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20definitely%20waiting%20for%20my%20green%20card%2C%20but%20that%20queue%20is%20not%20moving%20at%20all.%20It's%20been%20nine%20years%20now.%20I%20applied%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20came%20to%20the%20US.%20Nine%20years%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20moving.%20I%20wish%20it%20had%20been%20approved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-supporter-h-1b-visa-leaving-the-us-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758704402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cf1cd3183847aa39d72e96%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-supporter-h-1b-visa-leaving-the-us-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20software%20engineer%20from%20India%20says%20he's%20considering%20moving%20back%20home.%20The%20US%20feels%20too%20unstable%20after%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20H-1B%20fees%2C%20he%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22crollet%40insider.com%20(Charles%20Rollet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-supporter-h-1b-visa-leaving-the-us-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump's%20H-1B%20overhaul%20could%20kneecap%20startups%20in%20the%20talent%20wars.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227845%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20USA%20flag%20representing%20voters%20and%20citizenship.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d3395ef9db348adc0c0b26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrump's%20proposed%20H-1B%20changes%20have%20sent%20startups%20scrambling.%3Cp%3Ewildpixel%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20US%20startups%2C%20the%20past%20few%20days%20have%20felt%20like%20whiplash.%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-h-1b-visa-fee-silicon-valley-tech-hiring-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%24100%2C000%20H-1B%3C%2Fa%3E%20fee%20threw%20founders%20and%20their%20employees%20into%20chaos%2C%20and%20a%20fresh%20proposal%20to%20overhaul%20the%20visa%20lottery%20has%20left%20founders%20fearing%20they%20can't%20compete%20with%20deep-pocketed%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20for%20talent.%20Now%2C%20some%20young%20companies%20have%20frozen%20hiring%20as%20they%20scramble%20for%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20an%20employee%20who's%20been%20approved%20for%20H-1B%2C%20but%20he's%20abroad%2C%20so%20we%20were%20very%20scared%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Aizada%20Marat%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Alma%2C%20a%20legal%20tech%20startup%20that%20advises%20startups%20on%20visa%20issues%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20supposed%20to%20fly%20in%2C%20and%20we%20said%2C%20'Let's%20pause%20everything%2C%20let's%20get%20more%20clarification.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20unveiled%20a%20new%20proposal%20for%20the%20H-1B%20program%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20bases%20selection%20on%20skill%20level%20and%20wages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20and%20the%20fee%20increase%20could%20eventually%20be%20overturned%20by%20courts%2C%20but%20the%20ambiguity%20makes%20it%20hard%20for%20companies%20to%20make%20hiring%20decisions%2C%20according%20to%20Matt%20Hoffman%2C%20head%20of%20talent%20at%20the%20venture%20firm%20M13.%20He%20has%20been%20busy%20fielding%20calls%20from%20startup%20founders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20concern%20with%20all%20these%20policies%20being%20rolled%20out%20fairly%20haphazardly%20is%20that%20people%20don't%20have%20the%20certainty%20needed%20to%20make%20a%20significant%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoffman%20said.%20%26quot%3BIs%20there%20another%20shoe%20about%20to%20drop%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20Tech%20companies%20are%20by%20far%20the%20largest%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20H-1B%20program%20in%20the%20US%2C%20led%20by%20Amazon%2C%20which%20received%2014%2C667%20visas%20this%20year.%20But%20the%20proposed%20changes%20will%20have%20an%20outsized%20impact%20on%20smaller%20startups%2C%20according%20to%2010%20founders%20and%20investors%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Apple%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20or%20Google%2C%20%24100%2C000%20is%20peanuts%2C%26quot%3B%20Brian%20Hamilton%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Sageworks%20(now%20Abrigo)%2C%20wrote%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you're%20running%20a%20small%20technology%20company%20in%20a%20city%20like%20Raleigh%2C%20Austin%2C%20Atlanta%2C%20or%20Denver%2C%20it's%20a%20completely%20different%20story.%20The%20average%20salary%20for%20a%20software%20engineer%20in%20these%20places%20is%20closer%20to%20%24130%2C000%20to%20%24150%2C000.%20Adding%20another%20%24100%2C000%20is%20like%20doubling%20the%20cost%20of%20an%20engineer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarat%20says%20the%20new%20rules%20will%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20young%20startups%20to%20attract%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20with%20other%20well-funded%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYears%20ago%2C%20even%20OpenAI%20was%20a%20small%20startup.%20What%20if%20this%20rule%20prevents%20future%20OpenAIs%20and%20Anthropics%20from%20happening%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrustdata%20founder%20Chris%20Pisarski%20is%20having%20one-on-one%20calls%20with%20his%20H-1B%20employees.%20He%20thinks%20the%20policy%20will%20cause%20a%20skill%20gap%20in%20international%20hires%3A%20Startups%20will%20invest%20in%20senior-level%20talent%2C%20but%20stop%20bringing%20in%20younger%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20going%20to%20bring%20someone%20on%20that's%20entry-level%2C%20that's%20%2460%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20are%20you%20going%20to%20pay%20%24100%2C000%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20any%20companies%20will%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231a20995-77cb-4738-be42-863ee4d7a979%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESome%20tech%20founders%20welcome%20the%20H-1B%20changes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECongress%20created%20the%20H-1B%20program%20in%201990%20to%20allow%20American%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F40-tech-companies-sponsor-most-h-1b-immigrant-workers-visas-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20temporarily%20hire%3C%2Fa%3E%20highly%20skilled%20foreign%20workers%20for%20jobs%20that%20employers%20say%20can't%20be%20filled%20by%20US%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20startups%20use%20the%20program%20the%20most%2C%20though%20it%20is%20a%20fraction%20of%20their%20overall%20workforce%2C%20according%20to%20government%20data%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20TikTok%20owner%20ByteDance%20has%20the%20most%20H-1B%20approvals%20by%20far%20this%20year%2C%20with%201%2C360%20slots.%20Databricks%20came%20in%20second%20with%20248%2C%20then%20Stripe%20at%20151%2C%20and%20OpenAI%20at%2076.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F09%2Frestriction-on-entry-of-certain-nonimmigrant-workers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20that%20the%20H-1B%20system%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bdeliberately%20exploited%20to%20replace%2C%20rather%20than%20supplement%2C%20American%20workers%20with%20lower-paid%2C%20lower-skilled%20labor.%26quot%3B%20He%20pointed%20to%20IT%20outsourcing%20firms%20as%20the%20worst%20offenders%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20undercutting%20American%20wages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20prominent%20tech%20executives%20have%20praised%20the%20changes%2C%20with%20Netflix%20cofounder%20Reed%20Hastings%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Freedhastings%2Fstatus%2F1969828972688248953%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposting%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%20that%20the%20new%20fee%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20solution%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20reserve%20H-1B%20visas%20%26quot%3Bjust%20for%20very%20high%20value%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20(%3C%2Fstrong%3ENetflix%20was%20approved%20for%20208%20H-1B%20visas%20this%20year.%20It%20employs%20around%2014%2C000%20people%20worldwide.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-young-founders-ai-gold-rush-to-grow-up-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarvin%20von%20Hagen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20the%20Interaction%20Company%20of%20California%2C%20an%20AI%20agent%20startup%2C%20is%20also%20a%20fan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20in%20our%20circles%20see%20this%20as%20a%20positive%20because%20it%20has%20become%20easier%20to%20get%20a%20visa%2C%26quot%3B%20von%20Hagen%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20just%20need%20to%20pay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20Nasarin%2C%20a%20general%20partner%20at%20Tenacity%20Venture%20Capital%2C%20says%20the%20new%20rules%20will%20force%20startups%20to%20only%20use%20H-1B%20visas%20for%20the%20hardest-to-fill%20roles%2C%20which%20was%20the%20original%20intent%20of%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20believe%20startups%20consciously%20ignored%20US%20candidates%2C%20but%20the%20H-1B%20program%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20treat%20international%20and%20US%20candidates%20equally%2C%26quot%3B%20Nasarin%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20they%20will%20have%20to%20focus%20more%20on%20local%20talent%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20a%20bad%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-talent-wars-startups-compete-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20talent%20wars%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20made%20eye-popping%20compensation%20packages%20the%20norm%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%20To%20Shawn%20Shen%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20San%20Francisco%20AI%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FMemories.AI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMemories.AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20extra%20%24100%2C000%20fee%20is%20well%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-100k-h-1b-visa-trump-talent-company-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworth%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20right%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTalent%20is%20the%20single%20most%20important%20thing%20for%20startups%20now%20%E2%80%94%20if%20one%20person%20can%20execute%20really%2C%20really%20well%2C%20I%20think%20an%20additional%20%24100%2C000%20would%20be%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20their%20total%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20Shen's%20startup%20hasn't%20been%20impacted.%20His%20cofounder%2C%20Ben%20Zhou%2C%20is%20on%20an%20H-1B%20and%20was%20on%20his%20way%20back%20from%20a%20family%20trip%20to%20China%20when%20he%20learned%20of%20the%20new%20fees.%20His%20flight%20arrived%20in%20the%20US%20only%20hours%20before%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20deadline.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E(The%20White%20House%20has%20since%20clarified%20that%20the%20fees%20don't%20affect%20current%20H-1B%20holders.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShen%20thinks%20that%20for%20many%20founders%20outside%20the%20US%2C%20alternatives%20like%20the%20UK%20could%20become%20attractive.%20He%20says%20the%20visa%20process%20there%20is%20already%20a%20lot%20easier%20for%20them%20since%20it%20doesn't%20involve%20a%20lottery%20system%20like%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20signs%20that%20international%20tech%20hubs%20are%20taking%20advantage%20of%20the%20chaos%3A%20The%20UK%20is%20now%20considering%20scrapping%20visa%20fees%20for%20top%20talent%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Financial%20Times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fuk-explores-plan-drop-visa-fees-top-global-talent-ft-reports-2025-09-22%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsh%20Arora%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20LocalGlobe%2C%20said%20the%20new%20H-1B%20fees%20will%20push%20top%20talent%20from%20India%20to%20other%20hubs%20like%20the%20UK%20%E2%80%94%20even%20after%20the%20White%20House's%20clarifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClarifications%20don't%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIndian%20talent%20now%20sees%20US%20immigration%20as%20uncertain.%20People%20don't%20wait%20to%20see%20what%20will%20happen%3B%20they%20are%20risk-averse%20and%20will%20optimize%20for%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22baaaeb7b-b7e4-4c09-b168-3f3175805a65%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20O-1%20alternative%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20founders%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20said%20they%20would%20probably%20not%20hire%20more%20US%20workers%20if%20H-1B%20visas%20become%20scarcer%20and%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarat%20says%20that%20when%20she%20posts%20a%20job%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%2090%25%20of%20the%20applicants%20are%20outside%20the%20US%2C%20and%20those%20who%20are%20US%20citizens%20often%20lack%20the%20advanced%20computer%20science%20skills%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20passing%20the%20rigorous%20interviewing%20process%20we%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Marat%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20startup%2C%20you%20need%20to%20survive%2C%20you%20need%20to%20grow%2C%20and%20you%20just%20try%20to%20hire%20the%20best%20talent.%20There's%20nothing%20involved%20other%20than%20merit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarat%20said%20she%20will%20likely%20pursue%20other%20types%20of%20visas.%20One%20particularly%20popular%20with%20startups%20is%20the%20O-1%2C%20which%20allows%20people%20with%20%26quot%3Bextraordinary%20ability%26quot%3B%20to%20work%20for%20up%20to%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComposite%2C%20an%20AI%20browser%20startup%2C%20is%20less%20affected%20by%20the%20changes%20because%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bleaned