%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20late%20April%2C%20a%20full%20year%20since%20its%20launch%2C%20Q%20Developer's%20projected%20annual%20recurring%20revenue%20was%20%2416.3%20million%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20document%20obtained%20by%20BI.%20The%20forecast%20was%20based%20on%20roughly%20%24317%2C000%20in%20weekly%20revenue%20and%20%241.25%20million%20over%20the%20trailing%204-week%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EARR%20is%20a%20common%20industry%20metric%20that%20extrapolates%20weekly%20or%20monthly%20revenue%20streams%20into%20an%20annualized%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQ%20Developer's%20growth%20might%20have%20stood%20out%20in%20earlier%20years%2C%20but%20it%20looks%20modest%20in%20today's%20rapidly%20accelerating%20AI%20industry%2C%20according%20to%20Jason%20Lemkin%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20SaaStr%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Anysphere's%20Cursor%20coding%20tool%20crossed%20%24500%20million%20in%20ARR%20in%20June%20after%20reaching%20%24100%20million%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Another%20popular%20AI%20coding%20assistant%20Windsurf%20reported%20%2482%20million%20in%20ARR%20in%20July%2C%20less%20than%20a%20year%20into%20its%20launch.%20Even%20younger%20AI%20startups%20like%20Gamma%20and%20Higgsfield%20hit%20%2450%20million%20in%20ARR%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year%2C%20underscoring%20Q%20Developer's%20comparatively%20slower%20growth%2C%20Lemkin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20as%20jaw-dropping%20as%20it%20used%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Lemkin%20told%20BI%2C%20referring%20to%20Q%20Developer's%20growth.%20%26quot%3BAWS%20has%20fallen%20behind%20in%20the%20AI%20race.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bcontinuing%20to%20innovate%20rapidly%26quot%3B%20to%20grow%20Q%2C%20with%20firms%20including%20ADP%2C%20Deloitte%2C%20and%20Japan%20Research%20Institute%20among%20active%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20extremely%20pleased%20with%20the%20accelerating%20growth%20of%