sinsider.com%2Fgen-z-trust-issues-government-business-college-other-people-institutions-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeclines%20in%20trust%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20over%20decades.%20Add%20data%20breaches%2C%20convincing%20AI%20deepfakes%2C%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20transparency%20around%20how%20tech%20works%20and%20business%20operates%2C%20and%20it's%20easy%20to%20see%20why%20America%20is%20in%20a%20full-blown%20trust%20crisis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20try%20to%20repair%20the%20rift%2C%20some%20companies%20have%20added%20a%20new%20executive%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fso-many-executives-in-the-corporate-c-suite-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eever-bloating%20C-suite%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20has%20recently%20become%20home%20to%20chief%20experience%20officers%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdei-executives-linkedin-wayfair-how-get-jobs-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echief%20diversity%20officers%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctors-chief-medical-officers-healthcare-google-uber-salesforce-executives-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echief%20medical%20officers%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20latest%20addition%3A%20the%20chief%20trust%20officer.%20This%20small%20but%20growing%20cohort%20of%20tech%20experts%20is%20charged%20with%20working%20to%20protect%20data%2C%20answering%20questions%20around%20the%20efficacy%20and%20safety%20of%20AI%2C%20and%20building%20trust.%20The%20role%20comes%20with%20significant%20challenges%20for%20executives%20accustomed%20to%20leading%20with%20metrics%2C%20as%20trust%20is%20much%20more%20of%20a%20woolly%2C%20complex%20emotion%20than%20a%20metric.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParticularly%20thanks%20to%20AI%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20becoming%20harder%20to%20measure%20what's%20real%2C%20what's%20fake%2C%20and%20the%20trust%20boundaries%20are%20becoming%20more%20nebulous%2C%26quot%3B%20Lakshmi%20Hanspal%2C%20chief%20trust%20officer%20at%20the%20security%20company%20DigiCert%2C%20tells%20me.%20Cybersecurity%20is%20a%20defensive%20posture%2C%20and%20the%20chief%20information%20security%20officer%20(CISO)%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20C-suites%20for%2030%20years%2C%20has%20often%20been%20a%20reactive%20role%20responsible%20for%20responding%20when%20there's%20a%20cybersecurity%20threat%20or%20problem.%20CTrOs%2C%20as%20they're%20commonly%20known%2C%20are%20meant%20to%20be%20more%20proactive.%20The%20CTrOs%20I%20spoke%20to%20for%20this%20story%20say%20a%20typical%20cybersecurity%20team%20and%20checking%20off%20compliance%20boxes%20is%20not%20always%20enough%20for%20a%20company%20to%20convince%20its%20customers%20it's%20trustworthy%20anymore.%20A%20CTrO%20moves%20cybersecurity%20out%20of%20backrooms%20and%20into%20the%20business%20side%20of%20the%20company%20%E2%80%94%20that%20means%20their%20work%20is%20part%20technical%2C%20part%20communicative%2C%20and%20part%20innovative.%20They%20are%20tasked%20with%20safeguarding%20data%2C%20keeping%20companies%20compliant%20with%20regulations%2C%20ensuring%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-ethics-risks-responsibility-business-bcg-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eethical%20and%20accurate%20uses%20of%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20communicating%20all%20of%20this%20to%20customers%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20becoming%20more%20transparent%20and%20trustworthy.%20%26quot%3BIn%20an%20AI%20world%2C%20proof%20beats%20promise%2C%20and%20the%20CTrO%20owns%20the%20proof%2C%26quot%3B%20Hanspal%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20businesses%20are%20more%20trusted%20than%20non-government%20organizations%2C%20the%20media%2C%20and%20government%2C%20according%20to%20a%202024%20survey%20from%20public%20relations%20and%20marketing%20firm%20Edelman%2C%20overall%20trust%20is%20so%20low%20that%20they're%20all%20in%20a%20race%20to%20the%20bottom.%20Four%20in%2010%20people%20from%20across%20the%20globe%20who%20responded%20to%20Edelman's%202025%20survey%20said%20they%20approve%20of%20%26quot%3Bhostile%20activism%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20online%20attacks%2C%20damaging%20property%2C%20making%20threats%20of%20violence%2C%20or%20purposefully%20spreading%20misinformation%2C%20to%20bring%20about%20change.%20The%20public%20and%20business%20executives%20both%20want%20to%20have%20a%20trustworthy%20relationship%2C%20but%20they%20have%20completely%20different%20views%20on%20the%20current%20status%20of%20trust.%20In%20a%202024%20survey%20from%20accounting%20firm%20PwC%2C%2095%25%20of%20business%20executives%20say%20organizations%20have%20an%20obligation%20to%20build%20trust%2C%20and%2093%25%20say%20trust%20is%20good%20for%20the%20bottom%20line.%20The%20clash%3A%2090%25%20of%20executives%20said%20their%20companies%20yield%20high%20trust%20from%20customers%2C%20but%20only%2030%25%20of%20customers%20actually%20have%20high%20levels%20of%20trust%20in%20companies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrust%20is%20a%20thorny%20concept%20that's%20been%20entwined%20with%20the%20tech%20world%20since%20the%201990s.%20With%20more%20people%20plugging%20in%20their%20dial-up%20connections%20and%20the%20birth%20of%20user-generated%20content%2C%20being%20online%20meant%20more%20risk%20of%20scams%2C%20attacks%2C%20and%20misinformation%2C%20and%20companies%20had%20to%20focus%20on%20making%20their%20online%20experience%20palpable%20to%20people.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20trust%20across%20institutions%20took%20a%20hit.%20More%20than%20half%20of%20American%20adults%20trusted%20the%20government%20following%209%2F11%2C%20according%20to%20an%20analysis%20from%20Pew%20Research%20Center%2C%20but%20that%20number%20quickly%20dropped%20and%20has%20stayed%20below%2030%25%20since%202007.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-crisis-scariest-moments-2015-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2008%20financial%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20usurped%20trust%20in%20business%2C%20and%20those%20suspicions%20were%20exacerbated%20into%20the%202010s%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-protect-accounts-data-breach-password-leaks-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20breaches%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20became%20common.%20Over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20there's%20been%20pressure%2C%20especially%20for%20B2B%20companies%2C%20financial%20institutions%2C%20and%20the%20other%20organizations%20that%20handle%20sensitive%20data%2C%20to%20build%20trust%20back.%20The%20CTrO%20is%20coming%20as%20a%20reaction%20to%20that%20pressure.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20build%20this%20trust%20quickly%20so%20that%20we%20can%20continue%20to%20use%20these%20products%2C%20innovate%2C%20move%20quickly%2C%20differentiate%20our%20services%2C%20differentiate%20our%20companies%2C%20and%20just%20compete%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Chris%20Peake%2C%20chief%20trust%20officer%20at%20Gong%2C%20an%20AI%20revenue%20company.%20%26quot%3BIt%20not%20only%20became%20just%20an%20important%20risk%20to%20think%20about%20protecting%20the%20company%2C%20it%20became%20very%20much%20almost%20a%20business%20necessity%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Vinay%20Patel%2C%20software%20developer%20Zendesk%20as%20the%20company's%20first%20chief%20trust%20and%20security%20officer%2C%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BTrust%20is%20really%20the%20pillar%20upon%20which%20we%20can%20build%20and%20grow%20our%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chief%20trust%20officer%20is%20still%20a%20niche%20role.%20A%20recent%20report%20from%20Forrester%20Research%20looked%20at%2016%20chief%20trust%20officers%20and%20found%20their%20average%20tenure%20in%20the%20role%20to%20be%20just%20over%202%20years.%20But%20companies%20are%20steadily%20announcing%20they%20have%20hired%20those%20with%20backgrounds%20in%20cybersecurity%20roles.%20That's%20the%20profile%20Patel%20fits.%20He%20previously%20worked%20as%20a%20CISO%2C%20a%20role%20that%20also%20had%20its%20growth%20over%20the%20past%20few%20decades%20and%20is%20now%20commonplace.%20There's%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20to%20be%20a%20natural%20evolution%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20chief%20trust%20officer%20or%20some%20similar%20title%2C%20too%2C%20he%20says.%20As%20AI%20disrupts%20the%20workplace%2C%20CTrOs%20are%20needed%20to%20articulate%20what%20AI%20systems%20are%20built%20to%20do%2C%20and%20that%20they're%20being%20built%20responsibility.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20see%20that%20becoming%20more%20and%20more%20relevant%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20tells%20me%2C%20as%20customers%20will%20demand%20companies%20%26quot%3Bhave%20someone%20internally%20focused%20on%20ensuring%20that%20our%20trust%20isn't%20eroded%20every%20single%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20trust%20officers%2C%20AI%20is%20a%20two-pronged%20problem.%20There's%20nefarious%20actors%20using%20it%20for%20scams%2C%20but%20also%20skepticism%20that%20AI%20systems%20can%20be%20trusted%20to%20work%20ethically%20with%20sensitive%20data.%20The%20threat%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbank-account-scam-deepfakes-ai-voice-generator-crime-fraud-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeepfakes%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20one%20that%20sits%20outside%20of%20typical%20CISO%20work%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20securing%20tech%20systems.%20The%20widespread%20adoption%20of%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20generative%20AI%20tools%20like%20Midjourney%2C%20Dall-E%2C%20and%20video%20generators%20have%20made%20deepfakes%20easy%20and%20cheap%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years.%20Companies%20are%20facing%20not%20just%20cyber%20attacks%20to%20their%20infrastructure%2C%20but%20disinformation%20that%20can%20be%20spread%20about%20them%20online%2C%20and%20information%20attacks%20bolstered%20by%20AI%2C%20where%20people%20can%20impersonate%20company%20leadership.%20Ben%20Colman%2C%20CEO%20of%20deepfake%20detector%20company%20Reality%20Defender%2C%20says%20the%20CTrO%20or%20similar%20role%20can%20be%20someone%20who%20takes%20on%20conversations%20with%20regulators%20and%20publicly%20answers%20questions%20about%20security%20and%20safety.%20For%20some%20smaller%20companies%2C%20like%20Reality%20Defender%2C%20that%20means%20splitting%20up%20those%20functions%20across%20roles.%20But%20larger%20companies%20could%20increasingly%20hire%20a%20specific%20CTrO%20to%20wrangle%20them%20all.%20Colman%20says%20he%20views%20%26quot%3Banything%20to%20do%20to%20get%20people%20to%20take%20things%20like%20cybersecurity%20more%20seriously%20as%20a%20net%20positive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-warning-world-ai-replacing-jobs-necessary-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWidespread%20adoption%20of%20AI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20businesses%20that%20handle%20sensitive%20data%20is%20one%20way%20to%20gauge%20how%20well%20trust-building%20is%20going%2C%20but%20the%20starkest%20way%20to%20measure%20your%20trustworthiness%20is%20whether%20your%20customers%20stick%20with%20you%20or%20jump%20ship.%20Whether%20CTrOs%20do%20rebuild%20trust%20or%20add%20value%20for%20companies%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20%E2%80%94%20it%20could%20end%20up%20another%20flashy%20exec%20title%20that%20is%20a%20temporary%20bandaid%20to%20the%20bigger%20issue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20very%20least%2C%20the%20CTrO%20could%20be%20a%20way%20for%20companies%20to%20better%20communicate%20their%20goals%20and%20the%20tech%20that%20they're%20using%2C%20which%20is%20a%20more%20people-first%20starting%20point%20for%20rebuilding%20trust.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20separate%20the%20people%20from%20the%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20Peake%20says.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20really%20talking%20human%