whole%2C%20it%20isn't%20necessarily%20the%20most%20important%20at%20the%20organizational%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20just%20reduce%20compute%20to%20capital%2C%20you%20know%2C%20it's%20just%20money%2C%20and%20then%20you%20buy%20the%20physical%20infra%2C%26quot%3B%20Kwon%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20necessarily%20assume%20in%20lots%20of%20other%20industries%20or%20even%20in%20technology%20industries%20that%20if%20you're%20just%20the%20most%20capitalized%20company%20or%20organization%2C%20that%20you're%20automatically%20going%20to%20win.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20how%20you%20make%20use%20of%20that%20resource%20and%20apply%20it%20to%20various%20bets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKwon%20said%20that%20three%20things%20matter%20more%3A%20scarcity%2C%20bet%20selection%2C%20and%20organizational%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScarcity%20can%20sometimes%20create%20innovation%2C%20forcing%20sharper%20decisions%20about%20how%20to%20use%20limited%20resources%2C%20Kwon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBet%20selection%20%E2%80%94%20what%20kinds%20of%20research%20directions%20to%20pursue%2C%20when%20to%20double%20down%2C%20and%20when%20to%20pivot%20%E2%80%94%20is%20also%20what%20gives%20a%20lab%20its%20edge%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKwon%20said%20organizations%20need%20to%20have%20the%20right%20capacity%20or%20structure%20to%20make%20and%20sustain%20those%20bets%20well%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%20taste%20and%20selection%20criteria.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKwon%20and%20OpenAI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2a4c048-1484-4a9f-b930-9c670b7789be%5C%22%3EThe%20race%20for%20compute%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20country%20or%20industry%20level%2C%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20compute%2C%26quot%3B%20Kwon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompute%20is%20needed%20for%20%26quot%3Bthe%20breadth%20and%20diversity%20of%2