ng%20suspended%20over%20comments%20about%20Charlie%20Kirk.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESinclair%20and%20Nexstar%20still%20aren't%20airing%20Kimmel's%20show%20on%20their%20ABC%20affiliate%20stations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20hour%20before%20the%20show%20aired%2C%20Trump%20took%20to%20Truth%20Social%2C%20where%20he%20slammed%20Kimmel%20and%20ABC.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJimmy%20Kimmel%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjimmy-kimmel-back-on-abc-disney-after-suspension-fcc-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eback%20at%20ABC%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20late-night%20stage%20Tuesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKimmel%20walked%20out%20on%20stage%20to%20resounding%20cheers%20from%20the%20audience.%20His%20appearance%20on%20%26quot%3BJimmy%20Kimmel%20Live!%26quot%3B%20was%20his%20first%20public%20response%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabc-pulls-jimmy-kimmel-off-the-air-indefinitely-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EABC%20temporarily%20suspended%3C%2Fa%3E%20production%20of%20the%20show%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20want%20to%20thank%20all%20of%20you.%20You%20supported%20our%20show%2C%20cared%20enough%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it%2C%20to%20make%20your%20voices%20heard%20so%20that%20mine%20could%20be%20heard.%20I'll%20never%20forget%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Kimmel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20minutes%20into%20his%20monologue%2C%20Kimmel%20teared%20up%20and%20assured%20his%20audience%20that%20he%20never%20intended%20to%20make%20light%20of%20the%20killing%20of%20the%20conservative%20activist%20Charlie%20Kirk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20the%20truth%20is%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20what%20I%20have%20to%20say%20is%20gonna%20make%20much%20of%20a%20difference.%20If%20you%20like%20me%2C%20you%20like%20me.%20If%20you%20don't%2C%20you%20don't.%20I%20have%20no%20illusions%20about%20changing%20anyone's%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Kimmel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20show%20