-deserve-protection-hawley-launches-investigation-into-meta-for-training-its-ai-chatbots-to-target-children-with-sensual-conversation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESen.%20Josh%20Hawley%3C%2Fa%3E%20gave%20Meta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20until%20September%2019%20to%20provide%20every%20draft%20of%20a%20200-plus%20page%20internal%20rulebook%20that%20guided%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chatbots-hearing-big-tech-capitol-hill-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta's%20AI%20chatbots%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20and%20couldn't%20say%2C%20along%20with%20enforcement%20manuals%2C%20an%20age-gating%20system%2C%20and%20risk%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHawley's%20demand%20came%20after%20a%20Reuters%20investigation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Fmeta-ai-chatbot-guidelines%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20Meta's%20rules%20allowed%20bots%20to%20engage%20in%20provocative%20behavior%20that%20included%20sexual%20conversations%20with%20children.%20Meta%20removed%20that%20language%20and%20is%20training%20its%20chatbots%20to%20block%20inappropriate%20chats%20with%20teens%2C%20it%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Tuesday%2C%20Meta%20hadn't%20sent%20all%20the%20records%20and%20had%20not%20complied%20with%20Hawley's%20deadline%2C%20Hawley's%20spokesperson%20Bernadette%20Breslin%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Meta%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20finalized%20its%20first%20production%20of%20documents%20on%20Tuesday%20after%20resolving%20an%20unexpected%20transmission%20issue.%20They%20added%20that%20they%20plan%20to%20continue%20producing%20documents%20and%20look%20forward%20to%20working%20with%20Hawley's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22555eee04-9fb7-4a7e-806d-9b5439de13e9%5C%22%3EHawley's%20letter%20to%20Meta%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHawley%2C%20who%20chairs%20the%20Senate%20Judiciary%20Committee's%20Subcommittee%20on%20Crime%20and%20Counterterrorism%2C%20has%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20establish%20who%20approved%20the%20chatbot%20policies%2C%20how%20long%20they%20were%20in%20effect%2C%20and%20whether%20Meta%20misled%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20August%2015%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hawley.senate.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FHawley-Letter-to-Meta-re-AI-Chatbots-Engaging-Romantically-with-Kids.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20blasted%20Meta's%20rules%20as%20%26quot%3Breprehensible%20and%20outrageous%2C%26quot%3B%20pointing%20to%20examples%20where%20chatbots%20were%20permitted%20to%20describe%20an%20eight-year-old's%20body%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20work%20of%20art%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20masterpiece.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20warned%20that%20the%20investigation%20would%20examine%20whether%20Meta's%20generative%20AI%20products%20%26quot%3Benable%20exploitation%2C%20deception%2C%20or%20other%20criminal%20harms%20to%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2016%2C%20Hawley%20held%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hawley.senate.gov%2Ficymi-chairman-hawley-exposes-ai-chatbots-for-harming-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20expose%20what%20he%20characterized%20as%20growing%20harms%20to%20children%20posed%20by%20online%20chatbots%20made%20by%20Character.AI%2C%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%2C%20and%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20products%20are%20so%20great%20and%20so%20safe%2C%20then%20come%20defend%20your%20chatbots%20under%20oath%2C%26quot%3B%20Hawley%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1968061663380443550%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20day.%20%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20it's%20an%20open%20invitation.%20But%20it%20can%20be%20a%20subpoena.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scrutiny%20comes%20as%20Meta%20doubles%20down%20on%20its%20chatbot%20strategy.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Business%20Insider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-hires-contractors-build-ai-chatbot-characters-key-markets-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20company%20is%20hiring%20US-based%20contractors%20to%20help%20build%20character-driven%20bots%20for%20key%20growth%20markets%20such%20as%20India%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20and%20Mexico%2C%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20push%20to%20make%20AI%20companions%20central%20to%20its%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214eb27dd-b18a-4e04-aaf5-320a1c20d16f%5C%22%3EWhat%20Meta's%20missed%20deadline%20means%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20unusual%20for%20tech%20giants%20to%20blow%20past%20deadlines%20from%20Congress%2C%20where%20letters%20from%20lawmakers%20rarely%20carry%20enforcement%20power%20unless%20they're%20backed%20by%20a%20subpoena.%20Policy%20professors%20said%20Meta's%20silence%20is%20striking%20given%20the%20subject%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20upside%20to%20meeting%20the%20deadline%2C%20no%20consequence%20for%20missing%20it%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20more%20options%20from%20buying%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Alexis%20Wichowski%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20professional%20practice%20at%20Columbia%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20companies%20fear%20most%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20monstrously%20bad%20press%20that%20comes%20from%20revealing%20all%20the%20documents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWichowski%20pointed%20out%20that%20%3Cspan%3Enone%20of%20the%20many%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-scandals-last-decade-while-running-facebook-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econgressional%20investigations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Meta%20has%20faced%20since%202016%20have%20produced%20any%20real%20consequences%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20Kreps%2C%20a%20Cornell%20professor%20and%20director%20of%20its%20Tech%20Policy%20Institute%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20while%20Meta%20faces%20low%20legal%20risks%20from%20missing%20deadlines%2C%20it%20faces%20significant%20reputational%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20Meta%2C%20the%20stakes%20are%20higher%20because%20the%20underlying%20issue%20involves%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20Kreps%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20silence%20looks%20evasive%20and%20highlights%20how%20unprepared%20Meta%20seems%20for%20the%20responsibilities%20that%20come%20with%20deploying%20AI%20to%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20Pranav%20Dixit%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Apranavdixit%40protonmail.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Epranavdixit%40protonmail.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A14089059124%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E1-408-905-9124%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Contact%20Charles%20Rollet%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acrollet%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ecrollet%40insider.co%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cu%3Em%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20on%20Signal%20and%20WhatsApp%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A6282822811%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E628-282-2811%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cem%3E%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%