h%20cat%20company%20that%20offers%2011%20different%20recipes%2C%20including%20a%20smooth%20turkey%20pate.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20cat%20mom%20and%20pets%20reporter%20who%20researches%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-food%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20cat%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20extensively%2C%20I've%20learned%20that%20many%20cat%20foods%20will%20give%20your%20kitty%20the%20nutrition%20they%20need%2C%20just%20as%20long%20as%20they're%20complete%20and%20balanced%20for%20your%20cat's%20life%20stage.%20What%20sets%20certain%20cat%20food%20brands%20apart%20is%20their%20commitment%20to%20quality%20control%2C%20careful%20ingredient%20sourcing%2C%20and%20transparency.%20For%20pet%20parents%2C%20factors%20like%20ease%20of%20serving%20and%20storage%2C%20responsive%20customer%20service%2C%20and%20even%20how%20the%20food%20looks%20also%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmalls%20is%20one%20of%20a%20handful%20of%20fresh%20cat%20food%20companies%20that%20caught%20my%20attention.%20Made%20with%20gently%20cooked%20ingredients%2C%20it%20promised%20something%20different%2C%20so%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20for%20myself%20if%20it%20was%20worth%20all%20the%20buzz.%20My%20two%20cats%2C%20Atlas%20and%20Lyra%2C%20and%20I%20tried%20Smalls%20for%20a%20month%20in%202021%2C%20again%20in%202023%20when%20I%20compared%20cat%20food%20delivery%20services%2C%20and%20most%20recently%20in%20a%20month-long%20trial%20in%202025.%20After%20all%20that%20testing%2C%20it's%20still%20our%20favorite%20fresh%20cat%20food%20delivery%20service%2C%20and%20one%20I%20plan%20to%20keep%20in%20their%20regular%20rotation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2215cb326c-51da-4d6b-9cc8-5c9c1c88111f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20it%20works%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20it%20works%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202013%2C%20Smalls%20is%20a%20direct-to-consumer%20cat%20food%20delivery%20company%20that%20switched%20its%20focus%20exclusively%20to%20fresh%20in%202023.%20Unlike%20more%20processed%20commercial%20canned%20or%20dry%20cat%20food%2C%20%26quot%3Bfresh%26quot%3B%20food%20is%20made%20by%20combining%20and%20gently%20cooking%20whole%20meats%2C%20vegetables%2C%20and%20essential%20vitamins%20and%20minerals%2C%20then%20freezing%20the%20food%20to%20lock%20in%20freshness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecipes%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESmalls%20makes%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-55959-20%26h%3D28ace3f5d2e50e3a19f15b2b83ec1bc33298868fa0ae183b1794e2f9c9b765bc%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f4904b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fsmalls-cat-food-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.smalls.com%252Fwhy-smalls%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E11%20different%20fresh%20cat%20food%20recipes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20All%20of%20them%20are%20formulated%20to%20meet%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aafco.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAssociation%20of%20American%20Feed%20Control%20Officials%20(AAFCO)%3C%2Fa%3E%20standards%20for%20complete%20and%20balanced%20nutrition%20for%20all%20life%20stages%2C%20so%20they're%20appropriate%20for%20kittens%2C%20adults%2C%20and%20seniors%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Smalls%20doesn't%20employ%20an%20in-house%20veterinary%20nutritionist%20as%20recommended%20by%20the%20World%20Small%20Animal%20Veterinary%20Association%20(WSAVA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwsava.org%2Fglobal-guidelines%2Fglobal-nutrition-guidelines%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlobal%20Nutrition%20Guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20veterinarians%20I've%20consulted%20in%20my%20pet%20food%20reporting.%20That's%20why%20I%20didn't%20rank%20it%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-food%23best-fresh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20fresh%20cat%20food%20overall%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20spot%20earned%20by%20JustFood%20For%20Cats.%20Still%2C%20Smalls'%20recipes%20are%20developed%20by%20a%20consultant%20who%20has%20a%20PhD%20in%20animal%20nutrition%20and%20reviewed%20by%20board-certified%20veterinary%20nutritionists%2C%20all%20overseen%20by%20Dr.%20Sarah%20Mitten%2C%20a%20board-certified%20veterinarian%20who%20serves%20as%20Smalls'%20full-time%20veterinary%20advisor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIngredient%20sourcing%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESmalls%20sources%20chicken%2C%20turkey%2C%20pork%2C%20and%20beef%20in%20the%20US%2C%20while%20its%20fish%20comes%20from%20Japan.%20Vegetables%2C%20fruits%2C%20and%20oils%20are%20sourced%20worldwide%20from%20the%20regions%20where%20they%20grow%20best%2C%20and%20vitamins%20and%20minerals%20are%20also%20sourced%20globally%20but%20blended%20in%20the%20US%20to%20meet%20FDA%20requirements.%20These%20ingredients%20come%20together%20to%20create%20Smalls'%20recipes%2C%20which%20are%20cooked%20in%20third-party%2C%20USDA-approved%20facilities%20in%20New%20Jersey%20and%20Ohio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuality%20control%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EQuality%20control%20ensures%20that%20a%20food%20delivers%20the%20nutrients%20listed%20on%20the%20label%20and%20is%20free%20from%20harmful%20bacteria%2C%20contaminants%2C%20and%20toxins.%20Smalls%20tests%20every%20batch%20for%20Listeria%2C%20Salmonella%2C%20and%20E.%20coli%2C%20conducts%20annual%20checks%20for%20mercury%20and%20pesticides%2C%20and%20runs%20quarterly%20tests%20to%20verify%20nutrients%2C%20amino%20acids%2C%20and%20omega%20fatty%20acids%20are%20balanced%20and%20confirm%20heavy%20metals%20and%20vitamins%20remain%20at%20safe%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEach%20Smalls%20packet%20contains%20200%20calories%20and%20weighs%204.1%20to%205.5%20ounces.%20This%20amount%20is%20intended%20to%20feed%20an%20average%2010-pound%20cat%20for%20a%20day%2C%20but%20you%20should%20always%20check%20with%20your%20veterinarian%20to%20confirm%20your%20cat's%20caloric%20needs.%20Priced%20at%20%245%20to%20%245.50%20per%20packet%2C%20Smalls%20costs%20%240.30%20to%20%240.50%20more%20per%20ounce%20than%20premium%20wet%20food.%20Discounts%20kick%20in%20on%20any%20box%20larger%20than%20extra%20small%2C%20with%20savings%20increasing%20by%20size.%20The%20largest%20box%20is%2030%25%20off%2C%20dropping%20the%20price%20to%20about%20%240.70%20per%20ounce%2C%20right%20in%20line%20with%20premium%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-wet-cat-food%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewet%20cat%20food%20brands%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Shipping%20is%20free%20on%20all%20boxes%20bigger%20than%20extra%20small.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmalls%20also%20offers%20a%2030-day%20money-back%20guarantee%20on%20its%20Sampler%20box.%20But%20before%20you%20give%20up%2C%20the%20brand%20suggests%20transition%20strategies%20like%20warming%20the%20food%20or%20adding%20a%20topper.%20My%20cats%20especially%20enjoyed%20theirs%20with%20a%20splash%20of%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-55959-20%26h%3D5547c5f20213dad18e0d1d3072981a2111d4649ae73f70d401d2de10794bc0c7%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f4904b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fsmalls-cat-food-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.smalls.com%252Fsmallsmart%252Fproducts%252Ffish-broth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESmalls%20broth%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrdering%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESmalls%20is%20mostly%20direct-to-consumer%2C%20though%20you%20can%20find%20its%20food%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-55959-20%26h%3D63e20b0e719e34789e99e40b63554828d0e18c0b6dc80be01d46b6ee9f47e790%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f4904b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fsmalls-cat-food-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.smalls.com%252Fstores%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20brick-and-mortar%20pet%20stores%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20order%2C%20head%20to%20the%20Smalls%20website%20where%20you'll%20first%20answer%20a%20few%20questions%20about%20your%20cat%2C%20including%20their%20weight%2C%20age%2C%20spay-neuter%20status%2C%20allergies%20or%20protein%20aversions%2C%20and%20any%20health%20conditions%2C%20like%20urinary%20tract%20issues.%20If%20you're%20ordering%20for%20multiple%20cats%2C%20you'll%20complete%20the%20same%20questions%20for%20each%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECustomization%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDuring%20signup%2C%20you%20can%20exclude%20certain%20proteins%20from%20your%20Sampler%20box%2C%20but%20once%20you%20check%20out%2C%20your%20selection%20is%20locked.%20For%20future%20shipments%2C%20click%20the%20%26quot%3Bchange%20your%20box%26quot%3B%20option%20under%20the%20upcoming%20shipments%20section%20of%20your%20account%2C%20where%20you%20can%20add%20or%20remove%20items%2C%20skip%20shipments%2C%20or%20adjust%20your%20delivery%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShipping%20and%20delivery%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20you%20create%20a%20subscription%20plan%20and%20enter%20your%20cat's%20weight%2C%20Smalls%20calculates%20your%20cat's%20recommended%20daily%20calorie%20needs%20and%20adjusts%20your%20auto-ship%20frequency%20accordingly.%20You%20can%20also%20set%20delivery%20anywhere%20from%20weekly%20to%20every%2012%20weeks%2C%20with%20options%20to%20pause%2C%20skip%2C%20or%20cancel%20shipments.%20Smalls%20ships%20nationwide%2C%20except%20to%20Alaska%2C%20Hawaii%2C%20and%20PO%20boxes.%20Shipping%20is%20%2415%20for%20an%20extra%20small%20box%20or%20free%20for%20larger%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225553%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20open%20cardboard%20box%20contains%20Smalls%20cat%20food%20packs%2C%20a%20bag%20of%20cat%20treats%2C%20and%20informational%20inserts%2C%20including%20a%20card%20with%20a%20black-and-white%20cat%20photo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68cdbeba57d362d375e88e2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmalls%20packaging%20materials%20are%20recyclable%2C%20and%20the%20insulation%20is%20biodegradable.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPackaging%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESmalls%20meals%20ship%20with%20dry%20ice%2C%20biodegradable%20corn-based%20Styrofoam%2C%20and%20a%20recyclable%20cardboard%20box%20to%20maintain%20freshness%20for%20up%20to%20three%20days%20after%20shipping.%20To%20dispose%20of%20the%20packaging%2C%20remove%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreencellfoam.com%2Fdisposal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGreen%20Cell%20Plus%20(GC%2B)%3C%2Fa%3E%20film%20from%20the%20Styrofoam.%20The%20film%20and%20cardboard%20box%20can%20go%20in%20your%20recycling%20bin%2C%20while%20the%20Styrofoam%20dissolves%20in%20water%20or%20can%20be%20composted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ab85554c-fc33-4af3-9080-4ef3a02c7654%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20Smalls%20fresh%20cat%20food%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFiguring%20out%20how%20much%20cat%20food%20to%20order%20each%20month%20can%20be%20a%20chore.%20Too%20much%20leaves%20my%20cupboards%20overflowing%20with%20cans%20and%20kibbles%20or%20with%20a%20packed%20freezer%2C%20while%20too%20little%20means%20unhappy%20cats%20and%20last-minute%20store%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmalls%20simplified%20ordering%20and%20suggested%20a%20delivery%20schedule%20for%20its%20200-calorie%20packets%20based%20on%20my%20cats'%20weights%20(every%20two%20weeks%20for%20a%20medium-sized%20box).%20The%20serving%20recommendation%20was%20one%20packet%20per%20day%20for%20a%2010-pound%20cat.%20It's%20a%20good%20starting%20point%20if%20you're%20unsure%20how%20much%20to%20feed%2C%20but%20your%20veterinarian%20should%20ultimately%20determine%20the%20appropriate%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20checking%20out%2C%20I%20received%20a%20confirmation%20email%20right%20away%20with%20the%20option%20to%20edit%20my%20order.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20shipment%20tracking%20info%20landed%20in%20my%20email%2C%20and%20my%20food%20arrived%20frozen%20solid%20just%20three%20days%20later.%20It%20was%20packed%20in%20eco-friendly%20insulated%20foam%20and%20dry%20ice%2C%20giving%20me%20time%20to%20get%20it%20into%20the%20freezer%2C%20where%20it%20keeps%20for%20up%20to%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Plastic%20sealed%20pouches%20containing%20frozen%20at%20food%20from%20Smalls%20are%20arranged%20on%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d3282a57d362d375e8bb39%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221871%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmalls%20ships%20recipes%20frozen%20in%20plastic%20pouches%20and%20includes%20free%20treats%20with%20your%20order.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20pouches%20aren't%20resealable%2C%20their%20small%20size%20makes%20leftovers%20easy%20to%20store%20in%20an%20airtight%20container%20in%20the%20fridge%20and%20then%20feed%20within%20the%20recommended%20five%20days.%20I%20defrosted%20the%20packets%20in%20the%20fridge%20overnight%2C%20which%20took%20about%2012%20hours.%20Smalls%20also%20sent%20a%20reminder%20three%20days%20before%20my%20next%20shipment%20with%20options%20to%20edit%20or%20cancel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmalls%20offers%2011%20recipes%20with%20five%20different%20proteins%20(chicken%2C%20turkey%2C%20beef%2C%20pork%2C%20fish).%20Textures%20range%20from%20smooth%20pates%20to%20shredded%20and%20finely%20ground%20meats%20with%20veggies.%20The%20food%20is%20moist%20but%20slightly%20more%20crumbly%20than%20canned%20cat%20food%20and%20has%20a%20milder%20smell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyra%2C%20my%20cat%20who%20will%20eat%20just%20about%20anything%2C%20devoured%20every%20Smalls%20recipe.%20Atlas%2C%20who%20is%20my%20picky%20eater%2C%20needed%20a%20little%20nudge%20to%20try%20her%20food%2C%20and%20flat-out%20refused%20to%20eat%20a%20handful%20of%20the%20recipes.%20Fresh%20Smooth%20Fish%20was%20an%20obvious%20favorite%20of%20both%20cats%2C%20with%20Atlas%20gobbling%20it%20down%20without%20hesitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20is%20peeling%20back%20the%20label%20on%20a%20pouch%20of%20Smalls%20cat%20food%20beside%20a%20bowl%20holding%20some%20of%20the%20food%20along%20with%20other%20wet%20cat%20food.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d32ac757d362d375e8bb53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221873%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThough%20I%20transitioned%20my%20cats%20to%20Smalls%20food%20by%20combining%20it%20with%20their%20regular%20wet%20food%2C%20it%20took%20no%20coaxing%20to%20get%20them%20to%20eat%20the%20Smooth%20Fish%20recipe.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20appreciate%20that%20Smalls%20is%20transparent%20about%20ingredient%20sourcing%20and%20processing%2C%20which%20boosts%20my%20confidence%20in%20the%20quality%20and%20safety%20of%20its%20food.%20During%20a%20conversation%20with%20its%20Cat%20Concierge%2C%20which%20is%20Smalls'%20text-only%20customer%20service%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20its%20recipes%20use%20only%20organic%20minerals.%20These%20organic%20minerals%20contribute%20to%20a%20higher-quality%20diet%2C%20says%20Dr.%20Korinn%20Saker%2C%20a%20board-certified%20veterinary%20nutritionist%20and%20retired%20associate%20professor%20of%20clinical%20nutrition%20at%20the%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine%20at%20North%20Carolina%20State%20University.%20She%20says%20organic%20minerals%20are%20absorbed%20more%20readily%20by%20the%20body%20than%20inorganic%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20Cat%20Concierge%20also%20told%20me%20that%20the%20formulas%20contain%20dark%20meat%20chicken%20for%20a%20more%20enticing%20flavor%20than%20white%20meat.%20Nutritional%20yeast%20is%20added%20for%20a%20cheesy%20flavor%20and%20as%20an%20added%20source%20of%20protein%20and%20B%20vitamins.%20Each%20recipe%20also%20includes%20taurine%2C%20which%20is%20an%20essential%20amino%20acid%20that%20should%20be%20included%20in%20any%20diet%20you%20feed%20your%20cat.%20Cod%20liver%20oil%20is%20added%20for%20joint%2C%20skin%2C%20and%20coat%20health.%20Dandelion%20greens%2C%20an%20unusual%20addition%2C%20are%20beneficial%20too%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvetster.com%2Fen-us%2Fp%2Fjo-myers-salida-co-708ad60%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Jo%20Myers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veterinarian%20at%20Vetster.%20They're%20a%20good%20source%20of%20vitamins%20and%20minerals%2C%20including%20A%2C%20B%2C%20C%2C%20D%2C%20iron%2C%20potassium%2C%20and%20zinc.%20Just%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20too%20much%20of%20any%20supplement%20can%20be%20harmful%2C%20so%20if%20you're%20feeding%20your%20cat%20a%20complete%20and%20balanced%20diet%20such%20as%20this%20one%2C%20you%20do%20not%20need%20to%20give%20them%20additional%20nutrients%20in%20the%20form%20of%20supplements%20like%20fish%20oil%20or%20multivitamins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225553%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20gray%20and%20white%20cat%20eats%20from%20a%20yellow%20pedestal%20bowl%20sitting%20on%20top%20of%20a%20blue%20base.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d32b7357d362d375e8bb5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmalls%20sells%20attractive%20bowls%20on%20its%20website%2C%20but%20some%20cats%20may%20have%20difficulty%20accessing%20all%20of%20the%20food%20within%20the%20bowl.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20you%20can%20serve%20the%20food%20in%20Smalls'%20branded%20%2452%20elevated%20bowls%2C%20I%20don't%20recommend%20it.%20Though%20the%20bowls%20we%20tried%20were%20stylish%2C%20with%20a%20ceramic%20dish%20perched%20on%20a%20plastic%20pedestal%2C%20the%20plastic%20base%20on%20one%20of%20them%20warped%20in%20the%20dishwasher.%20The%20bowl%20also%20has%20a%20convex%20rather%20than%20concave%20design%2C%20so%20food%20slides%20to%20the%20sides%20instead%20of%20staying%20centered.%20My%20cats%20finished%20their%20meals%2C%20but%20had%20to%20press%20their%20faces%20into%20the%20sides.%20This%20could%20frustrate%20some%20cats%20or%20prevent%20flat-faced%20(brachycephalic)%20breeds%20from%20eating%20comfortably.%20If%20you%20do%20decide%20to%20purchase%20one%2C%20watch%20your%20cat%20closely%20to%20ensure%20they%20are%20comfortable%20with%20the%20bowl%20and%20wash%20by%20hand%20to%20ensure%20the%20plastic%20pedestal%20isn't%20damaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5040c05-a924-43fe-b8a8-c5eb47d86293%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20select%20%26quot%3Byes%26quot%3B%20for%20certain%20medical%20conditions%20during%20signup%2C%20Smalls%20claims%20its%20food%20is%20%26quot%3Bgood%26quot%3B%20for%20cats%20with%20issues%20such%20as%20arthritis%2C%20cancer%2C%20epilepsy%2C%20diabetes%2C%20cystitis%2C%20or%20asthma.%20However%2C%20your%20veterinarian%20is%20the%20best%20resource%20for%20determining%20which%20food%20is%20appropriate%20for%20your%20cat's%20medical%20needs.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20brand%20does%20consult%20with%20animal%20nutritionists%2C%20board-certified%20veterinary%20nutritionists%2C%20and%20has%20a%20full-time%20veterinary%20advisor.%20However%2C%20because%20Smalls%20does%20not%20employ%20a%20veterinary%20nutritionist%20as%20recommended%20by%20the%20WSAVA%20Global%20Nutrition%20Guidelines%2C%20I%20recommend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-55959-20%26h%3De2b9aff05e017caffeecdc3f50bf47aee29e52727aead49a638bdfccbe089823%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f4904b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fsmalls-cat-food-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.justfoodfordogs.com%252Fproduct%252Ffish-and-chicken-for-cats%252F30040107.html%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJustFood%20For%20Cats%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20best%20fresh%20cat%20food%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmalls%20suggests%20a%20shipping%20schedule%20based%20on%20your%20cat's%20needs%2C%20but%20meals%20aren't%20preportioned.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpetnutritionalliance.org%2Fresources%2Fcalorie-calculator%3Ftype%3Dcats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPet%20Nutrition%20Alliance%3C%2Fa%3E%20recommends%20261%20calories%20for%20a%2010-pound%20cat%2C%20while%20my%20vet%20suggested%20220%20for%20my%2010-pound%20cat%2C%20Lyra.%20For%20my%20two%20cats%2C%20Smalls'%20estimate%20was%20about%2040%20calories%20short%20of%20what%20they%20actually%20eat.%20Even%20so%2C%20the%20subscription%20still%20provided%20us%20enough%20food%2C%20with%20about%20a%20four-day%20buffer%20of%20leftovers%20between%20shipments.%20You%20can%20adjust%20the%20delivery%20schedule%20if%20you%20prefer%20more%20or%20less%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20questions%20about%20recipes%2C%20feeding%20guides%2C%20or%20shipping%2C%20you%20can%20text%20Smalls'%20Cat%20Concierge%20or%20email%20the%20brand.%20Texts%20go%20to%20a%20bot%20first%2C%20so%20you%20must%20request%20a%20human.%20Replies%20work%20more%20like%20email%20than%20live%20chat%2C%20sometimes%20taking%20up%20to%2018%20hours.%20The%20brand%20does%20not%20offer%20phone%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf790d11-1fe4-4e4c-b039-0cff876ee0b3%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20little%20evidence%20that%20cats%20fed%20fresh%20or%20human-grade%20diets%20are%20healthier%20than%20those%20eating%20nutritionally%20complete%20and%20balanced%20commercial%20dry%20or%20wet%20food.%20Still%2C%20it%20can%20feel%20good%20to%20feed%20ou